# Eval case: subscription-auditor

IDEA="Build a local tool that detects recurring subscriptions and silent price hikes from imported bank and card statements. A deterministic engine clusters transactions by merchant and cadence to identify recurring charges, flags amount increases, and estimates annualized spend. A local LLM writes a plain-English cancellation-priority summary from the structured findings only. Output a Markdown subscription audit report."

CONTEXT="Target: single user, laptop-only, no cloud sync. Stack: Python CLI; Pandas; DuckDB (encrypted); Ollama 8B optional. Formats: 2 CSV templates (bank, credit card). Limits: max 3 statement sources; detection window 24 months. Non-goals: auto-cancellation; bank API linking; cloud LLM default; React UI; multi-user; tax filing; PDF/charts; transmitting transactions to any LLM. Defer: email-receipt parsing; reminder notifications; mobile app."
